text: Hi all, I won't be able to make it to tomorrow's TSC call as I'm on site with a client...for agenda item regarding CI Options I'd like to recommend Go-CD (<https://www.go.cd/>) if we plan on building many multiple projects and pipelines. I've been a part of teams with robust Go-CD pipelines and it's a really great tool for pipeline orchestration of more complex workflows
